title: Ryan Learning Center
copy: Please fill out our inquiry form to learn more about rental opportunities.   Available Friday–Wednesday, 6:00–11:30 p.m. Capacity: 25 classroom, 57 studios Featuring three large studios and five classrooms, the Ryan Learning Center offers an ideal setting for meetings, presentations, and small-group breakout sessions. From arts and crafts tables to multimedia displays, these versatile spaces are equipped to accommodate a wide range of needs and activities.
